author: stsp
msg: Fix issue #3727, "svn export into the current directory".
This regression was introduced in r988064. Apparently due to an error
during conflict resolution, parts of r880559 were merged, a revision
which wasn't supposed to be part of the merge.
Also merge the regression test for issue #3727 from trunk.
(export_to_current_dir): Merge this test from trunk and resolve a
conflict caused by a difference between trunk and 1.6.x in the
(svn_cl__export): Do not special-case the empty path. Fixes the regression.
